   Image Commander is a full-featured software that allows you to add text or image watermarks to any picture. Protect your copyrights with a copyright notice or your logo. Add text and comments to any image. Create advanced thumbnails with cool styles and effects. Prepare your image collections to be published on the web. Resize, crop and rotate thumbnails. Batch processing thousands of images. There is support for BMP, JPG, GIF, PNG, TIFF and PSD image types.

* Protect your copyright:
   Using Image Commander you can add text or a logo as a watermark to your images. You can change many watermark's properties in WYSIWYG mode.

* Create cool thumbnails:
   Image Commander can create advanced thumbnails with cool styles and effects like dropping shadow, bevel, glow and more. 

* Crop, resize or rotate images:
   Image Commander will allow you to resize, crop and rotate images in batch mode. Image Commander support for BMP, JPG, GIF, PNG and TIFF image types on Windows platform and BMP, JPG, GIF, PNG, TIFF. (and PSD image types on Mac OS X in newer versions)

* Cross-platform:
   Image Commander full support for Microsoft Windows XP & Vista. (Mac OS in later versions) Image Commander has the look, feel, and function identically on both operating systems, each running the same underlying engine.
